Well its a month later after I intally posted my findings I have my epic and this time I was able to do some tests again with another level 60 mage.<br>
<br>
The Epic pet gets a run for its money 1 in 15 times so far against MS3.<br>
<br>
What I mean by this is Epic pet ends up down to 10 percent health or less.<br>
<br>
As for against MOBs the epic beats other pets hands down.<br>
<br>
The example I can give is the Dino in OOT.  I can solo him with epic in under 1 min just healing him a few times with our new heal spell.  Can't do this with MS3 as well, takes usually 2 times the heals.<br>
